Supplemental Table 1 – supplement of Figure 3. Unique Operational Taxonomic Units (OTUs) in NOD_vehicle compared to NOD_baseline. GreenGenes v13-8 OTU IDs and taxonomy for OTUs present in NOD mice gavaged with vehicle for 14 days not found in the same animals at baseline (n= 3 samples per time-point).
